After spending two weeks inside with my sick son climbing on the wall not even able to take a shower in peace i took a sigh of relif when i left him over in his fathers care till friday  yesterday. To never get that break, to always have all the responsobility all alone...that takes alot of strenght!<br>
so, if you do it all by your self, Be DAMN proud of your self. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Roosiesig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
